trans-unit.source: Contains values used as identifiers by <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IGridProvider"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder verdier som brukes som identifikatorer av <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IGridProvider"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: These identifiers are used by UI Automation providers.
trans-unit.target: Disse identifikatorene som brukes av Brukergrensesnittet Automation leverandører.

trans-unit.source: UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent fields in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern>.
trans-unit.target: Brukergrensesnittet Automation klientprogrammer skal bruke de tilsvarende feltene i <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern>

trans-unit.source: Identifies the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IGridProvider.ColumnCount*> property.

trans-unit.source: Hidden rows and columns, depending on the provider implementation, may be loaded in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] tree and will therefore be reflected in the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern.GridPatternInformation.RowCount%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern.GridPatternInformation.ColumnCount%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Skjulte rader og kolonner, avhengig av implementeringen leverandøren kan lastes inn i den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] tre og vil derfor gjenspeiles i den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern.GridPatternInformation.RowCount%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern.GridPatternInformation.ColumnCount%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern.GridPatternInformation.ColumnCount%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern.GridPatternInformation.RowCount%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the hidden rows and columns have not yet been loaded they are not be counted.
trans-unit.target: Hvis skjulte rader og kolonner ikke er lastet skal de ikke telles.

trans-unit.source: The default value is 0.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er 0.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.
